text: Nanteuil is a commune in the Deux-Sèvres department in western France. It may also refer to: *Nanteuil-le-Haudouin, a comune in the Oise a department in northern France *Nanteuil, Vichel-Nanteuil, a village in a commune in the Aisne department in northern France
title: Nanteuil (disambiguation)
